{"tid":1745290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清潔理大義工團","createTime":"2019-11-22T06:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T09:20:05.000Z","uid":337569,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a18c86127a4eddf72d64461f12a2022acd378c4","tid":1745290,"uid":337569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"清潔香港 人人有責<br />\n<br />\n如果想幫手清潔理大 有冇機會可以組織個義工團入去學校？政府圍左學校咁耐用左咁多兵力 小市民想出一分力幫手 眼見個校園被破壞得咁嚴重 都想快d恢復番原狀<br />\n<br />\n有冇得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa62e2eb0f84dd84a309a6aff9adf28d773f31d","tid":1745290,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f57419c5a75fbe92d093730d2b97b6cf61ca68e","tid":1745290,"uid":252877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"樓主直接入去咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e98d1485f652976fde99a05d6baafe78d74c3f","tid":1745290,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去五個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依五個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyln4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=6a8ef0cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85f65e7c4c59237afff7c541493820bc16ae821","tid":1745290,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qE2qASe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqE2qASe.png&h=9af35617&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44be698053a135048ba7fbdbd8be34850b4a5642","tid":1745290,"uid":337569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f57419c5a75fbe92d093730d2b97b6cf61ca68e","tid":1745290,"uid":252877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"樓主直接入去咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"仲入唔入到去？"},{"pid":"a6c13b0e818fb1a8f03172147c025961e2324a43","tid":1745290,"uid":252877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44be698053a135048ba7fbdbd8be34850b4a5642","tid":1745290,"uid":337569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f57419c5a75fbe92d093730d2b97b6cf61ca68e","tid":1745290,"uid":252877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"樓主直接入去咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"仲入唔入到去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:20:05.000Z","msg":"如果你係警務處長就應該得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}